item.title: Error_game_js5connect
item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

error_game_js5connect usually means that it does not recognize a ip online anymore to connect or there is something in the client that only lets host connect to 127.0.0.1. Utorrent is not a good way to portfoward half the time it doesn’t work. I guess since your using utorrent check on canyouseeme.org to see if your port is open on 43595. And if it is open send the client to a friend with the no-ip and see if they get the same error.
